data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Hunter's Creek, Florida! This stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers over 2200 square feet of luxurious living space, providing the perfect blend of comfort and style.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm embrace of a meticulously designed open-concept layout, seamlessly connecting the spacious living, dining, and kitchen areas. The new vinyl luxury plank flooring not only adds a touch of modern elegance but also ensures easy maintenance and durability for years to come.    One of the features of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen, all the appliances you need for day-to-day living, ample counter space, and a convenient bar. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or prefer casual dining, this space is sure to inspire your inner chef.    Natural light floods the interiors, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere throughout. Imagine waking up to sun-kissed mornings and enjoying the scenic views of the adjacent golf course from the comfort of your own home.    This residence is not only aesthetically pleasing but also practical, with a complete replumb in 2021 and a brand-new roof installed in 2022, ensuring peace of mind for the years ahead.     Nestled in a private gated community with a dedicated gate guard, security and exclusivity are paramount. Experience the tranquility of suburban living while still being close to all the conveniences Hunter's Creek has to offer. Plus, as an added bonus, the HOA handles the landscaping for the front yard, providing a manicured look you're going to love.    Indulge in the Florida lifestyle with this exceptional property that seamlessly combines modern amenities, natural beauty, and a prime location. Your dream home awaits in Hunter's Creek—schedule a showing today and step into a life of comfort, style, and sophistication!
